  "hashesWithUnresolvedText": {
    "9355e5998c86619bcdd626d5b7eb5c7427ac98187c65cd73319b3d05bdd6bbdd": {
      "text": "[player name]? I didn't recogonise you in all that Mourner gear!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "1e9be2dbda779fd607437d24bc42e84eb353b3f60d9b331a5458c4c9048629d8": {
      "text": "[player name]? I didn't recognise you in all that Mourner gear!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "2cc0ffa47735f72a095ce247ce149c97ba847c3ead3c849b56858f6bbd38043d": {
      "text": "[player name]! How's it going? Have you found out any more about the plague?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "616c09d3b325ec072d4ddbae34cf50dee080ebb155454adcdb12a89c71eab16f": {
      "text": "Is that you [player name]?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "7de919eec9321920790f3e8f38a09767e857d10ddaf5a2505e35ed42bf7e95d8": {
      "text": "Hello [player name]. Have you found out what those mourners are up to yet?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "9cd4fc042e117a27fa99df1c4967c0c17409a1aad5e41c0cac6041dcd64233a6": {
      "text": "[player name]? What are you doing here?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "dec0ad7cae81c52b491a0b2ff90538006f17741ab20cc53dc14e89f5f4234f16": {
      "text": "Ah [player name], thank goodness. How's it going?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "8a2c790d363fa972f5d26c4ad4e0a8dea8c51c0652b1b105db9f34ebc09dbc2e": {
      "text": "Now's not the time for games [player name]!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "837ecd919acabb1a209562548b85df9958cfb247799c440aa74a0a0ea2bf3e24": {
      "text": "[player name]!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "42eb8fdfeffdbdd1d244de9c36e00d9356e316c53de8ef5d034c424fd73271e6": {
      "text": "And you [player name]. Thank you so much for helping to get me out of there.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "e45e20844a2df9fc193edfa1c44482451b4d6e820287101546d138802f6acc80": {
      "text": "I care about you as well, [player name]. Thank you for not forgetting about me.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "a30af8b5d1d046f9edae2caa72a7fa4ff972b205581c31ed31aee1e266afa219": {
      "text": "This, [player name], is the Ardougne Resistance!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "7e2c28191afa316be45dda832dea370b023934d73b731ce5aa4644b6f103d2e7": {
      "text": "Hey. We've recruited [number] people into the resistance so far. We still need [number] more.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[number]",
        "[number]"
      ]
    },
    "c07468afe243f4c88fa659f6f436586b84ac75cf79d3028d9633003cf72471c7": {
      "text": "[player name] is innocent in this. You manipulated them for your own gain.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "9da96963e538ce667c29b1e269d0dde5eff48ea610b0b5614148d165b941279e": {
      "text": "[player name] is innocent! You lied to them!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "1237bc88ab216a72a732df712a59dab0eeffd513c127603d027d01cbf63fd20f": {
      "text": "The people of Ardougne, the elves here, you've spent a lot of time helping them. Why? What drives you, [player name]?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "721ccec32b7ed9c437c22bc9d09479393e3b37cac960991530118989893d1cc5": {
      "text": "I guess it's always nice to be rewarded. You should be careful not to let that drive you though. Money can't buy everything, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "c3bb9e18b4678490b3b2fe0756347a33d6a6aaf8875c042b81309107de70538a": {
      "text": "You should be careful of letting that drive you. Money can't buy everything, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "aef1cc8c9d8aec702f699853142990fa8eff4cff82914291ab3ecb57cf52fa94": {
      "text": "So the only thing driving you is guilt? That doesn't seem healthy. Be careful that you don't carry the world on your shoulders, [player name]. It's not your fault that Lathas manipulated you.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "c9c455107ca00a5a41f19b33129bdbc0f4c2e28451cd7e01f510134cf26f172c": {
      "text": "Hmmm, not something you've had to think about I guess. Just make sure that you don't carry the world on your shoulders, [player name]. It's not your fault that Lathas manipulated you.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "87176aeb016712691b651ce545a0c5f7c0cb8856d395dd5403284f13032b27e5": {
      "text": "Hey [player name]. You should talk to Arianwyn when you're ready to begin.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "f6067069e9d26761c3c40a4d416d5d9f8ae6e80dc063f38f9e972aced7eb2bcc": {
      "text": "Hey [player name]. Good to see you.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "91824636d78f118bd120637cb72e9896b135984f3410a4a536c738233d800ae3": {
      "text": "Right. [player name], meet me by the pond. I could use your help with this.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "bcedf8e92ef056141f4f4f6fe7b32b84eb42fa03abd9884f277b10b52a1b9936": {
      "text": "Hey [player name]. Glad everything went okay at Baxtorian Falls.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "bed9913f0f3390b6c7a87c31a0d404f5499eb67d1f7d6edc076fbc91774691d7": {
      "text": "Hey [player name]. Do you have that seed yet?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "6876d7a8bc2e78006ef201449aa72da8138c6fbf8508855fb8ef218479d121c4": {
      "text": "Hey [player name]. The elder cadantine herb grew perfectly. Let's get it harvested.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "6c999e894159affb3a922cbc9f7e6d505fcfc1f5f68d608ce3eee1a8c18b30ce": {
      "text": "Hey [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "b28894548b858ed077037be6110161c921f3e4f023d6e9fd82b14e0f91d00581": {
      "text": "Hey [player name] Good luck in the library. We'll talk more when you get back.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "9bca0672ea1ea1015baacbdca21b3e714555de548ef9eaf33b7dacb92ce86085": {
      "text": "Hey [player name]. You'd better speak with Arianwyn if you're done in the library.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "a576ea57552687503506f3d4a2b2805c291fe74f1ba1c320e0413858f9624b49": {
      "text": "Hey [player name]. Thanks for the talk earlier, it meant a lot. I won't keep you, I'm sure you've got things to do. See you later",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "ba9d521d0b26ef4dd5146428b78e9da37e3e688e03cad63460ec00c9632c5139": {
      "text": "[player name], you go help Mawrth. We'll get the other citizens to safety.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "b4572a31fbdeb136e4d0d38efb1f4794a4e2587dc2dd9cf1ce78a879bbe4bd22": {
      "text": "[player name]...",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "26436931cff71a527c4c9458f0027c771745607228038521d7b789e2d390e904": {
      "text": "Thank you [player name], you're a good friend.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "6c6b35514bd7ef10ec92f28633757a70603200d15e229c5e5f7b72cfc742c662": {
      "text": "Good luck [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "7b1a7171b7024b9049acf0addff249a5f4d55bf96e7fd8848f91db9ce0b2c375": {
